# Environment variables (local development)

Copy to `.env.local` and fill in values from `npx convex dev`:

```env
# Written by `npx convex dev` — your personal dev deployment
NEXT_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL=https://your-dev-deployment.convex.cloud

# Local app URL (must match Convex SITE_URL for auth cookies)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

## Convex dashboard (dev deployment)

Set via `npx @convex-dev/auth` or Convex dashboard:

- `SITE_URL` — same as `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL`
- `JWT_PRIVATE_KEY`, `JWKS` — generated by `npx @convex-dev/auth`
- `OWNER_EMAILS`, `ADMIN_EMAILS` — comma-separated promotion emails
- `STRIPE_SECRET_KEY`, `STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET` — optional

## Vercel (production only)

- `NEXT_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL` — production Convex URL (e.g. `https://precious-duck-100.eu-west-1.convex.cloud`)
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` — live site URL (e.g. `https://www.someducation.com`)

Do **not** commit `.env.local` to git.
